item.title: By: ljedi
item.dc:creator: ljedi
item.description: I always felt that way when I visited UNM. Something about moving on to a different place in your life (not necessarily physically) can make things disorienting when you are in a past environment. Still, it was great to see you! (And yes, I haven't read your blog in a while! Bad me)
